== Articles about individuals ==

Heyo, indeed. Thanks for the amazing work you are doing for the VRChat Wiki so far. One of the Guidelines we have in place, is that articles about individual users, and creators are not permitted on the Wiki. This topic is being brought up, in regards to the "STUDIO JINGO" page that has been removed recently. I took some of the useful information from that article, and transferred it to the [[Community:Rindo]] article.

VRCWiki information about the guideline for "not writing about others" is currently in the [[VRCWiki:How to Contribute]] article, but I'll also place it in the actual [[VRCWiki:Guidelines]] page tomorrow. Thanks again for your help so far. Feel free to reply back, or message me on the VRChat Wiki Discord server if you would like to follow up. [[User:Usr 8ee44c1a-f905-4e08-bb61-e1cd34e09fc0|Usr 8ee44c1a-f905-4e08-bb61-e1cd34e09fc0]] ([[User talk:Usr 8ee44c1a-f905-4e08-bb61-e1cd34e09fc0|talk]]) 04:58, 13 November 2024 (UTC)

